Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:18.93,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Fallin' fallin' love now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:24.48,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}這就是命中注定…Oh my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:32.11,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不會讓你說你沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.65,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}1,2…heart beat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:37.45,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在星辰大海中唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.99,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只屬於我的命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:44.41,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若是動了真情  怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:43.45,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(你又會)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.33,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用盡全心全意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.67,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去尋找未來的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:58.51,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在你那裡找到了  不會消去的夢之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:04.39,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}假如世界停轉一天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.77,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(在停轉之時)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:11.81,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}請一直一直抱緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.81,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(緊緊抱著我)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.03,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}盡想著這些任性的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.82,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}對不起…喜歡你「沒有極限」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:22.74,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不要害怕  明天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.07,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 heart!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.49,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(1,2 beat!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.99,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}希望可以確認你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:26.70,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fs17}(UN-DELAYED)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:34.29,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用觸及的指尖接受我熱情的奇蹟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.30,opcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}UN-DELAYED, Oh my love!
